  "lore": {
    "key": "Tbl_Unit_Desc_53",
    "english": "Taimanin. He was an elite ninja of the Igawa clan and taught Taimanin Art to Asagi when she was young. Wears a full suit of armor and wields the longsword \"Abara\" which glows an eerie crimson and heavy chains as weapons.\n\nA master of the \"Momochi Style\", a derivative swordsmanship which he developed himself. He is considered one of the strongest close-combat fighters within the Igawa clan.",
    "japanese": "Taimanin. He was an elite ninja of the Igawa clan and taught Taimanin Art to Asagi when she was young. Wears a full suit of armor and wields the longsword \"Abara\" which glows an eerie crimson and heavy chains as weapons.\n\nA master of the \"Momochi Style\", a derivative swordsmanship which he developed himself. He is considered one of the strongest close-combat fighters within the Igawa clan.",
    "korean": "Taimanin. He was an elite ninja of the Igawa clan and taught Taimanin Art to Asagi when she was young. Wears a full suit of armor and wields the longsword \"Abara\" which glows an eerie crimson and heavy chains as weapons.\n\nA master of the \"Momochi Style\", a derivative swordsmanship which he developed himself. He is considered one of the strongest close-combat fighters within the Igawa clan.",
    "chinese_simplified": "Taimanin. He was an elite ninja of the Igawa clan and taught Taimanin Art to Asagi when she was young. Wears a full suit of armor and wields the longsword \"Abara\" which glows an eerie crimson and heavy chains as weapons.\n\nA master of the \"Momochi Style\", a derivative swordsmanship which he developed himself. He is considered one of the strongest close-combat fighters within the Igawa clan.",
    "chinese_traditional": "Taimanin. He was an elite ninja of the Igawa clan and taught Taimanin Art to Asagi when she was young. Wears a full suit of armor and wields the longsword \"Abara\" which glows an eerie crimson and heavy chains as weapons.\n\nA master of the \"Momochi Style\", a derivative swordsmanship which he developed himself. He is considered one of the strongest close-combat fighters within the Igawa clan.",
    "spanish": "Taimanin. He was an elite ninja of the Igawa clan and taught Taimanin Art to Asagi when she was young. Wears a full suit of armor and wields the longsword \"Abara\" which glows an eerie crimson and heavy chains as weapons.\n\nA master of the \"Momochi Style\", a derivative swordsmanship which he developed himself. He is considered one of the strongest close-combat fighters within the Igawa clan."
